Prompt Engineering Internship — Task 1
AI Website Copy Generator for Local Businesses
Business Type: Cafe / Restaurant  |  Tone: Professional & Trustworthy
Submitted by: Pallavi Ashireddy  |  CIN: FIT/MAR26/PE2233
Repository: FUTURE_PE_01  |  Date: 30/03/2026

1. Project Overview
This document presents a complete AI-generated website copy set for a local Cafe/Restaurant business. The copy covers three core website sections: Homepage, Services/Menu Page, and CTA (Call-to-Action). Each section was generated using carefully structured prompts fed into Claude (claude.ai). The prompt logic, iterative refinements, and final outputs are fully documented below for transparency and reproducibility.

2. Prompt Engineering Strategy
The following framework was used to design each prompt for maximum output quality:

•Role Assignment — The AI was told to act as a professional website copywriter.
•Business Context — Specific business type (cafe/restaurant), location type, and target audience were provided.
•Tone Instruction — A professional and trustworthy tone was explicitly specified.
•Output Format — The desired structure (headline, subheadline, body copy, CTA) was defined.
•Constraints — Word limits and readability requirements were included in each prompt.

3. Homepage Copy
3.1 Prompt Used
🎯 Homepage Copy Prompt
PROMPT:
You are a professional website copywriter specializing in local businesses. Write homepage copy for a cafe/restaurant called "The Golden Brew" located in Hyderabad. The tone should be professional and trustworthy. Include: (1) A compelling headline, (2) A subheadline that builds trust, (3) A 60-word value proposition paragraph, and (4) Two short supporting statements. The content should appeal to professionals, families, and food lovers. Keep it website-ready and conversion-focused.
AI OUTPUT:
Headline: "Where Every Visit Feels Like Home — And Every Bite Tells a Story"
Subheadline: Hyderabad's most trusted neighbourhood cafe, serving quality meals since 2018.
Value Proposition: At The Golden Brew, we believe great food is more than a meal — it is an experience worth returning to. From our hand-crafted beverages to our chef-curated menu, every dish is prepared with premium ingredients, genuine care, and a commitment to consistency. Whether you are here for a morning coffee or a family dinner, expect nothing less than excellence.
Support 1: Rated 4.8/5 by over 2,000 satisfied guests across Hyderabad.
Support 2: Fresh, locally sourced ingredients — prepared daily, served with pride.

3.2 Final Homepage Copy
HEADLINE
Where Every Visit Feels Like Home — And Every Bite Tells a Story

Hyderabad's most trusted neighbourhood cafe, serving quality meals since 2018.

At The Golden Brew, we believe great food is more than a meal — it is an experience worth returning to. From our hand-crafted beverages to our chef-curated menu, every dish is prepared with premium ingredients, genuine care, and a commitment to consistency. Whether you are here for a morning coffee or a family dinner, expect nothing less than excellence.

✔  Rated 4.8/5 by over 2,000 satisfied guests across Hyderabad.
✔  Fresh, locally sourced ingredients — prepared daily, served with pride.


4. Services / Menu Page Copy
4.1 Prompt Used
🎯 Services Page Prompt
PROMPT:
You are a professional copywriter for a cafe/restaurant website. Write the "Our Menu" page copy for "The Golden Brew" in Hyderabad. Tone: professional and trustworthy. Include: (1) A page headline, (2) A short intro paragraph (40 words), (3) Descriptions for 4 menu categories — Breakfast, All-Day Beverages, Lunch & Dinner, and Desserts. Each description should be 25–35 words, persuasive, and highlight quality and taste. Avoid cliches. Be specific and appetising.
AI OUTPUT:
Page Headline: "A Menu Built on Quality, Crafted for Every Craving"
Intro: Explore a thoughtfully curated selection of dishes and beverages, designed to satisfy every palate. At The Golden Brew, quality is non-negotiable — from the first sip of your morning coffee to your last dessert bite.
Breakfast: Start your morning with a purpose. Our breakfast menu offers protein-rich platters, artisan toast selections, freshly brewed filter coffee, and wholesome options — all prepared to order, every single morning.
All-Day Beverages: From single-origin pour-overs to house-blend cold brews and signature lemonades, our beverage bar is crafted for those who take their drinks seriously. Available from open to close.
Lunch & Dinner: Our lunch and dinner offerings bring bold flavours to familiar comfort food. Slow-cooked curries, grilled mains, fresh salads, and chef's specials — updated seasonally to keep your palate curious.
Desserts: End perfectly. Our dessert menu features classic confections and contemporary creations — each made in-house with premium dairy, seasonal fruits, and a touch of culinary artistry.

4.2 Final Services Page Copy
A Menu Built on Quality, Crafted for Every Craving
Explore a thoughtfully curated selection of dishes and beverages, designed to satisfy every palate. At The Golden Brew, quality is non-negotiable — from the first sip of your morning coffee to your last dessert bite.

🌅 Breakfast
